name: R'tic H'weei
Text: 'Once per game, may take one Jawa Blaster or a card with ''sandcrawler'' in title or gametext into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. If present at a Tatooine battleground, once per turn, if there is more than 1 card in opponent''s Force Pile, may use 1 Force in opponent''s Force Pile.',
